[The chikungunya virus outbreak in French Polynesia is increasing rapidly, and placing stress on medical services. The virus has spread to several islands in French Polynesia. In the absence of a commercially available vaccine, vector control is the only preventive measure available.

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map showing the location of the islands in French Polynesia can be accessed at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2957255,382. - Mod.TY]
